</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="178" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,1768,1867]" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">
Phylogenetic evidence strongly supports inclusion of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pilger" authorityYear="1914" box="[754,938,1768,1794]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Couepia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipendula">
<emphasis box="[754,938,1768,1794]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">C. longipendula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<emphasis box="[980,1053,1768,1794]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Aublet" authorityYear="1775" box="[980,1049,1768,1794]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Acioa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Acioa</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Although 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Prance" authorityYear="1974" box="[1176,1352,1768,1794]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Couepia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dolichopoda">
<emphasis box="[1176,1352,1768,1794]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">C. dolichopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not included in this study, the morphological similarities between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pilger" authorityYear="1914" box="[837,1019,1804,1830]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Couepia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipendula">
<emphasis box="[837,1019,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">C. longipendula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Prance" authorityYear="1974" box="[1074,1248,1804,1830]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Couepia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dolichopoda">
<emphasis box="[1074,1248,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">C. dolichopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are extensive and in themselves sufficient to warrant also including 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Prance" authorityYear="1974" box="[695,867,1840,1866]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Couepia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dolichopoda">
<emphasis box="[695,867,1840,1866]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">C. dolichopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Aublet" authorityYear="1775" box="[903,968,1840,1866]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chrysobalanaceae" genus="Acioa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="178" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[903,968,1840,1866]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="178">Acioa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
